---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Section from '../../components/Section.astro';

const lang = 'pl';
---

<BaseLayout
  lang={lang}
  title="Kontakt | Archigiliti"
  description="Porozmawiajmy o Twoim projekcie. Architektura IT, AI, doradztwo technologiczne."
>
  <Section variant="light" class="pt-12 md:pt-16">
    <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="mb-6">Porozmawiajmy</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-neutral-mid dark:text-stone-400">Masz pytanie? Chcesz omówić projekt? Napisz — odpowiadam osobiście.</p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section variant="default">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <a href="mailto:piotr.andrasz@archigiliti.com" aria-label="Wyślij e-mail na adres piotr.andrasz@archigiliti.com" class="group p-8 bg-neutral-light dark:bg-surface-dark rounded-xl border border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-700 hover:border-primary/30 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 text-center cursor-pointer">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M21.75 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25 2.25h-15a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.25-2.25V6.75m19.5 0A2.25 2.25 0 0019.5 4.5h-15a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25m19.5 0v.243a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07 1.916l-7.5 4.615a2.25 2.25 0 01-2.36 0L3.32 8.91a2.25 2.25 0 01-1.07-1.916V6.75"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-dark dark:text-neutral-light mb-2">E-mail</h3>
          <p class="text-primary font-medium">piotr.andrasz@archigiliti.com</p>
        </a>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/piotr-andrasz-90510813/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" aria-label="Otwórz profil LinkedIn Piotra Andrasza (otwiera się w nowej karcie)" class="group p-8 bg-neutral-light dark:bg-surface-dark rounded-xl border border-stone-200 dark:border-stone-700 hover:border-primary/30 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 text-center cursor-pointer">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-primary/10 flex items-center justify-center text-primary group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-colors duration-300">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-dark dark:text-neutral-light mb-2">LinkedIn</h3>
          <p class="text-primary font-medium inline-flex items-center gap-1">Piotr Andrasz <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14"/></svg></p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section variant="light">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
      <h2 class="mb-8">Co dalej?</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div>
          <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center font-semibold">1</div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">Napisz do mnie</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-mid dark:text-stone-400">Opisz krótko swój kontekst i czego szukasz.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center font-semibold">2</div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">Umówimy rozmowę</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-mid dark:text-stone-400">30-45 minut, bez zobowiązań. Zrozumiem Twoje potrzeby.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="w-10 h-10 mx-auto mb-4 rounded-full bg-primary text-white flex items-center justify-center font-semibold">3</div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold mb-2">Propozycja</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-neutral-mid dark:text-stone-400">Jeśli mogę pomóc — przedstawię konkretny plan działania.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section variant="default">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-12">Często zadawane pytania</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <details class="group bg-neutral-light dark:bg-surface-dark rounded-lg">
          <summary class="p-6 cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between text-base font-semibold text-neutral-dark dark:text-neutral-light hover:text-primary transition-colors">
            Czy realizujecie wdrożenia?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-neutral-mid group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6">
            <p class="text-neutral-mid dark:text-stone-400">Tak, ale zawsze zaczynamy od architektury i decyzji. Nie wdrażamy bez planu.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="group bg-neutral-light dark:bg-surface-dark rounded-lg">
          <summary class="p-6 cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between text-base font-semibold text-neutral-dark dark:text-neutral-light hover:text-primary transition-colors">
            Czy pracujecie z zespołami klienta?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-neutral-mid group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6">
            <p class="text-neutral-mid dark:text-stone-400">Tak — transfer wiedzy jest kluczowy. Działamy jako rozszerzenie Twojego zespołu.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
        <details class="group bg-neutral-light dark:bg-surface-dark rounded-lg">
          <summary class="p-6 cursor-pointer list-none flex items-center justify-between text-base font-semibold text-neutral-dark dark:text-neutral-light hover:text-primary transition-colors">
            Czy AI to tylko LLM?
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-neutral-mid group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform duration-200" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
          </summary>
          <div class="px-6 pb-6">
            <p class="text-neutral-mid dark:text-stone-400">Nie. AI to narzędzie, nie cel sam w sobie. Pomagamy wybrać właściwe rozwiązanie do problemu.</p>
          </div>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>
</BaseLayout>
